n政府一刀切 ! 市民一獲熟 ! <br />\n高官下台 ! 政府賠錢 ! </span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n由於港府不封關<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">任由中共蝗進出香港關口造成嚴重公眾衛生安全</span> ! <br />\n衛生署同入境署既檢疫方法仲有<span style=\"color: violet;\">家居自我隔離</span>簡直完全同無掩雞籠完全無分別 ! <br />\n<br />\n亦多次被廣大市民於網上拍攝到<span style=\"color: pink;\">帶隔離手帶者於市區公眾地方四處遊蕩</span> ! <br />\n而且自我隔離機制仲有<span style=\"color: red;\">入境伸報機制完全係自願式</span> 即係有同無係無分別 !<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港府完全將香港市民生命財產安全視為糞土 !</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n在此我地召集大家一齊<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>集氣成立民間苦主組織並同時控告入稟索償香港政府</strong></span>及其中個別部門既無能而造成既金錢損失 ! <br />\n單係強制停業令已經令一眾市民蒙受巨大既金錢損失 !  更令一眾打工仔失業 , 無工返！<br />\n<br />\n係疫症期間 , 所有失業 倒閉 都係由於<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港政府拒絕實施全面性封關所導致</span></span></strong> !<br />\n<br />\n另外 直到近日政府既舒困措施對現時實際被影響既<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大眾打工仔一啲實際幫助</span></span></strong>都無 ! <br />\n完全只係為左俾老細交租而做既手法 <br />\n只係為左保住香港既樓市泡沫 而且棄民生於不顧<br />\n而且派錢係講緊<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">半年後 半年後</span></strong>你都餓死左啦 ! <br />\n而且錢仲係直接俾傭主而唔係你 ! <br />\n即係佢可以係呢半年入面抄左你之後袋袋平安 ! <br />\n派口罩都隔幾個月先派 真係個毒流行左你都病死左啦 !  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地借鑑目前外國做法<br />\n於是我地發起聯署 <br />\n藉由被疫情影響既大眾集氣控告追討政府抗疫不力而導致既一連串經濟下滑 ! <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 控告香港政府賠償損失 ! <br />\n我地要你賠錢 !  我地要你下台 ! </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地想捉成各業界同工會組成苦主作為代表向政府追討實際損失 <br />\n以及我地都想徵收一下法律性意見<br />\n呢份聯置收集完成後 會交俾有關組織作為協助追究之用<br />\n<br />\n聯署 : <br />\n我地首要放左上 <a href=\"http://change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchange.org&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=2cb546e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">change.org</a> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">控告同追討香港政府抗疫不力而造成既經濟損失</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/8ygCHY4F9p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2F8ygCHY4F9p&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=4034f332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/8ygCHY4F9p</a><br />\n<br />\n如果大家有時間既可以填埋 呢份google form<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdLph7ay7DSH8HEkXNaUid0wb4T3LWFfsEMgwFM0Y2GDH5QoA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdLph7ay7DSH8HEkXNaUid0wb4T3LWFfsEMgwFM0Y2GDH5QoA%2Fviewform&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=11f0cb43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdLph7ay7DSH8HEkXNaUid0wb4T3LWFfsEMgwFM0Y2GDH5QoA/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n#2為國際戰線行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀<br />\n【全城禁聚】 政府一刀切業界白交過百萬租 陳國明：三成桌球室會執笠 ｜ 即時 ｜ 體育 ｜ 20200502<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200502/JZ666IQTNJUWZDQ4OTRHTCVSK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200502%2FJZ666IQTNJUWZDQ4OTRHTCVSK4%2F&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=d7c394e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200502%2FJZ666IQTNJUWZDQ4OTRHTCVSK4%2F&h=327c7b2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200502/JZ666IQTNJUWZDQ4OTRHTCVSK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n【限聚令】停業令延長14日 美容業：剎停復工準備失預算<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2623384/%E3%80%90%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4%E3%80%91%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD%E4%BB%A4%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B714%E6%97%A5%E3%80%80%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%B9%E6%A5%AD%EF%BC%9A%E5%89%8E%E5%81%9C%E5%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%A4%B1%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2623384%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E3%2580%25